//    1.  absmean computation
//    2.  ternary quantization values ⊂ {-1, 0, 1}
//    3.  absmean thresholding rule
//    4.  dequantize = gamma * q
//    5.  round-trip MSE bound
//    6.  zero-vector edge case
//    7.  constant-vector edge case
//    8.  STE backward identity region
//    9.  STE backward clip region
//   10.  train-step descent direction
//   11.  matmul ternary vs dense equivalence
//   12.  matmul shape correctness
//   13.  memory ratio ~= 10x (FP16 baseline)
//   14.  packed vs unpacked storage
//   15.  nonzero ratio sanity
//   16.  quantization-error SNR positive on random data
